MULTIPLIER_DIVISOR().details: Return the divisor used to correctly calculate multiplier.	Multiplier stored throughout AO contracts covers 6 decimals,	so 1 is 1000000, 0.023 is 23000, etc

PERCENTAGE_DIVISOR().details: Return the divisor used to correctly calculate percentage.	Percentage stored throughout AO contracts covers 4 decimals,	so 1% is 10000, 1.25% is 12500, etc

calculateMaximumBurnAmount(uint256,uint2.details: Calculate the maximum amount of Primordial an account can burn	_primordialBalance = P	_currentWeightedMultiplier = M	_maximumMultiplier = S	_amountToBurn = B	B = ((S x P) - (P x M)) / S

params._maximumMultiplier: The maximum multiplier of this account

calculateMultiplierAfterBurn(uint256,uin.details: Calculate the new multiplier after burning primordial ion	_primordialBalance = P	_currentWeightedMultiplier = M	_amountToBurn = B	_newMultiplier = E	E = (P x M) / (P - B)

params._amountToBurn: The amount of primordial ion to burn

calculateMultiplierAfterConversion(uint2.details: Calculate the new multiplier after converting network ion to primordial ion	_primordialBalance = P	_currentWeightedMultiplier = M	_amountToConvert = C	_newMultiplier = E	E = (P x M) / (P + C)

params._amountToConvert: The amount of network ion to convert

calculateNetworkBonusAmount(uint256,uint.details: Calculate the bonus amount of network ion on a given lot	AO Bonus Amount = B% x P

params._endingMultiplier: The ending Network ion bonus multiplier
params._purchaseAmount: The amount of primordial ion intended to be purchased
params._startingMultiplier: The starting Network ion bonus multiplier
params._totalPrimordialMinted: Total Primordial ion minted so far

calculateNetworkBonusPercentage(uint256,.details: Calculate the bonus percentage of network ion on a given lot	Total Primordial Mintable = T	Total Primordial Minted = M	Starting Network Bonus Multiplier = Bs	Ending Network Bonus Multiplier = Be	To Purchase = P	AO Bonus % = B% = (1 - ((M + P/2) / T)) x (Bs-Be)

params._endingMultiplier: The ending Network ion bonus multiplier
params._purchaseAmount: The amount of primordial ion intended to be purchased
params._startingMultiplier: The starting Network ion bonus multiplier
params._totalPrimordialMinted: Total Primordial ion minted so far

calculatePrimordialMultiplier(uint256,ui.details: Calculate the primordial ion multiplier on a given lot	Total Primordial Mintable = T	Total Primordial Minted = M	Starting Multiplier = S	Ending Multiplier = E	To Purchase = P	Multiplier for next Lot of Amount = (1 - ((M + P/2) / T)) x (S-E)

params._purchaseAmount: The amount of primordial ion intended to be purchased
params._totalPrimordialMinted: Total Primordial ion minted so far

calculateWeightedMultiplier(uint256,uint.details: Calculate the new weighted multiplier when adding `_additionalPrimordialAmount` at `_additionalWeightedMultiplier` to the current `_currentPrimordialBalance` at `_currentWeightedMultiplier`

params._additionalPrimordialAmount: The primordial ion amount to be added
params._additionalWeightedMultiplier: The weighted multiplier to be added

params._contentId: The contentId related to this Name
params._keyValue: The key/value pair to be checked on the database
params._originId: The eth address the creates the Name

params._contentId: The contentId related to this TAO
params._keyValue: The key/value pair to be checked on the database
params._originId: The Name ID the creates the TAO
